                    <span>"What Color Is Your Parachute" is the best weapon in a job seeker's arsenal.  "Parachute" provides tips and insight for the first time job seeker as well as those who have been displaced, downsized or found shifting careers.  And especially in these times of economic hardship, this book will help the job hunter inventory their skills and talents.  With so many seeking so few positions, this book can be the difference maker for you.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">This book works!</div>
